    "chemicalDescription": [
      "Oligopeptide-123 rh-Oligopeptide-1 is a single chain synthetic fusion peptide, produced by fermentation in  E. coli.  The starting gene is synthesized by the fusion of the gene from rh-Oligopeptide-1 and Oligopeptide-123. The fusion peptide contains 67 amino acids and consists of the proper sequence of the 20 standard amino acids."
